title: Acer launches an RTX 40-series laptop you might actually be able to afford
description: A gaming laptop with an RTX 40-series GPU that doesn't cost a fortune? Apparently, it can be done, and Acer has just unveiled one.

title: No more GPUs? Here’s what Nvidia’s DLSS 10 could look like
description: Nvidia has just teased the future of DLSS, and it looks like the feature alone might one day be powerful enough to replace a whole team of people.

title: Spotify using AI to clone and translate podcasters’ voices
description: A new Spotify feature powered by artificial intelligence translates a podcast into multiple languages using the same voices of those in the show.

title: NASA’s Mars rover uses its self-driving smarts to navigate toughest route
description: As it continues its search for signs of ancient microbial life, NASA's Mars rover recently used its self-driving smarts to navigate its trickiest route yet.

title: NASA is seeking help to crash the space station at the end of its life
description: NASA is seeking help to build a space tug that will be deployed to safely deorbit the International Space Station at the end of its life in 2031.
